"Psionic Prodigy"  
        This is a global power modifier allowing the psionicist to learn
        new powers more rapidly.  It requires planning ahead to use this
        power effectively. From the point it is learned onwards the
        psionicist will gain 1 extra purchase point per level. 
        Once learned, this may not be forgotten.
 
SP Cost:  none		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  none
